{
  "video_id": "3wxBTEo8-T8",
  "title": "4 larger-than-life lessons from soap operas | Kate Adams",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 16560.0,
      "text": "In 1987, Tina Lord found herself in quite the pickle."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16560.0,
      "end_time": 19880.0,
      "text": "See, this gold digger made sure she married sweet Cord Roberts"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19880.0,
      "end_time": 22560.0,
      "text": "just before he inherited millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22560.0,
      "end_time": 24800.0,
      "text": "But when Cord found out Tina loved his money"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24800.0,
      "end_time": 26440.0,
      "text": "as much as she loved him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26440.0,
      "end_time": 27720.0,
      "text": "he dumped her."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27720.0,
      "end_time": 29640.0,
      "text": "Cord&#39;s mother Maria was thrilled"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29640.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "until they hooked up again."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31160.0,
      "end_time": 33840.0,
      "text": "So Maria hired Max Holden to romance Tina"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33840.0,
      "end_time": 37600.0,
      "text": "and then made sure Cord didn&#39;t find out Tina was pregnant with his baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37600.0,
      "end_time": 40520.0,
      "text": "So Tina, still married but thinking Cord didn&#39;t love her"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40520.0,
      "end_time": 42720.0,
      "text": "flew to Argentina with Max."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42720.0,
      "end_time": 44840.0,
      "text": "Cord finally figured out what was going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44840.0,
      "end_time": 47840.0,
      "text": "and rushed after them, but he was too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47840.0,
      "end_time": 49440.0,
      "text": "Tina had already been kidnapped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49440.0,
      "end_time": 52360.0,
      "text": "strapped to a raft and sent over a waterfall."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52360.0,
      "end_time": 55320.0,
      "text": "She and her baby were presumed dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55320.0,
      "end_time": 58360.0,
      "text": "Cord was sad for a bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58360.0,
      "end_time": 59840.0,
      "text": "but then he bounced right back"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59840.0,
      "end_time": 63240.0,
      "text": "with a supersmart archaeologist named Kate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63240.0,
      "end_time": 64760.0,
      "text": "and they had a gorgeous wedding"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64760.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69080.0,
      "text": "until Tina, seemingly back from the dead, ran into the church holding a baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69080.0,
      "end_time": 71200.0,
      "text": "&quot;Stop!&quot; she screamed."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71200.0,
      "end_time": 72720.0,
      "text": "&quot;Am I too late?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72720.0,
      "end_time": 75600.0,
      "text": "Cord, I&#39;ve come so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75600.0,
      "end_time": 79400.0,
      "text": "This is your son.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79400.0,
      "end_time": 80920.0,
      "text": "And that, ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80920.0,
      "end_time": 84120.0,
      "text": "is how the soap opera &quot;One Life to Live&quot; introduced a love story"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84120.0,
      "end_time": 86200.0,
      "text": "that lasted 25 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86200.0,
      "end_time": 87560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87560.0,
      "end_time": 89680.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;ve ever seen a soap opera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89680.0,
      "end_time": 94600.0,
      "text": "you know the stories and the characters can be exaggerated, larger than life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94600.0,
      "end_time": 97880.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re a fan, you find that exaggeration fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97880.0,
      "end_time": 99600.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99600.0,
      "end_time": 102320.0,
      "text": "maybe you find them melodramatic or unsophisticated."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102320.0,
      "end_time": 104560.0,
      "text": "Maybe you think watching soap operas"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104560.0,
      "end_time": 105840.0,
      "text": "is a waste of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105840.0,
      "end_time": 110560.0,
      "text": "that their bigness means their lessons are small or nonexistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110560.0,
      "end_time": 113440.0,
      "text": "But I believe the opposite to be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113440.0,
      "end_time": 117920.0,
      "text": "Soap operas reflect life, just bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117920.0,
      "end_time": 121360.0,
      "text": "So there are real life lessons we can learn from soap operas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121360.0,
      "end_time": 124200.0,
      "text": "and those lessons are as big and adventurous"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124200.0,
      "end_time": 127320.0,
      "text": "as any soap opera storyline."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127320.0,
      "end_time": 130920.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ve been a fan since I ran home from the bus stop in second grade"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130919.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133640.0,
      "text": "desperate to catch the end of Luke and Laura&#39;s wedding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133640.0,
      "end_time": 137040.0,
      "text": "the biggest moment in &quot;General Hospital&quot; history."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137040.0,
      "end_time": 138320.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138320.0,
      "end_time": 141680.0,
      "text": "So you can imagine how much I loved my eight years"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141680.0,
      "end_time": 144680.0,
      "text": "as the assistant casting director on &quot;As the World Turns.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144680.0,
      "end_time": 146720.0,
      "text": "My job was watching soap operas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146720.0,
      "end_time": 148160.0,
      "text": "reading soap opera scripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148160.0,
      "end_time": 150960.0,
      "text": "and auditioning actors to be on soap operas."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150960.0,
      "end_time": 153280.0,
      "text": "So I know my stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153280.0,
      "end_time": 154560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 154560.0,
      "end_time": 156880.0,
      "text": "And yes, soap operas"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 156880.0,
      "end_time": 159200.0,
      "text": "are larger than life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 159200.0,
      "end_time": 160920.0,
      "text": "drama on a grand scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 160920.0,
      "end_time": 164680.0,
      "text": "but our lives can be filled with as much intensity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164680.0,
      "end_time": 167840.0,
      "text": "and the stakes can feel just as dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167840.0,
      "end_time": 170160.0,
      "text": "We cycle through tragedy and joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 170160.0,
      "end_time": 172120.0,
      "text": "just like these characters."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 172120.0,
      "end_time": 176600.0,
      "text": "We cross thresholds, fight demons and find salvation unexpectedly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176600.0,
      "end_time": 179600.0,
      "text": "and we do it again and again and again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 179600.0,
      "end_time": 182360.0,
      "text": "but just like soaps, we can flip the script,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 184640.0,
      "text": "which means we can learn from these characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 184640.0,
      "end_time": 186480.0,
      "text": "that move like bumblebees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186480.0,
      "end_time": 189080.0,
      "text": "looping and swerving through life."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 189080.0,
      "end_time": 191360.0,
      "text": "And we can use those lessons"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 191360.0,
      "end_time": 193880.0,
      "text": "to craft our own life stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 193880.0,
      "end_time": 197600.0,
      "text": "Soap operas teach us to push away doubt"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 197600.0,
      "end_time": 199800.0,
      "text": "and believe in our capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 199800.0,
      "end_time": 202440.0,
      "text": "for bravery, vulnerability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 202440.0,
      "end_time": 205280.0,
      "text": "adaptability and resilience."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205280.0,
      "end_time": 207600.0,
      "text": "And most importantly, they show us"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 207600.0,
      "end_time": 211120.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s never too late to change your story."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 214120.0,
      "text": "So with that, let&#39;s start with soap opera lesson one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214120.0,
      "end_time": 216120.0,
      "text": "surrender is not an option."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216120.0,
      "end_time": 218120.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 218120.0,
      "end_time": 222720.0,
      "text": "&quot;All My Children&quot;&#39;s Erica Kane was daytime&#39;s version of Scarlett O&#39;Hara,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 222720.0,
      "end_time": 225200.0,
      "text": "a hyperbolically self-important princess"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225200.0,
      "end_time": 228800.0,
      "text": "who deep down was scrappy and daring."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228800.0,
      "end_time": 232440.0,
      "text": "Now, in her 41 years on TV, perhaps Erica&#39;s most famous scene"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232440.0,
      "end_time": 234440.0,
      "text": "is her alone in the woods"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234440.0,
      "end_time": 237200.0,
      "text": "suddenly face to face with a grizzly bear."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237200.0,
      "end_time": 239480.0,
      "text": "She screamed at the bear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239480.0,
      "end_time": 240920.0,
      "text": "&quot;You may not do this!"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 240920.0,
      "end_time": 242600.0,
      "text": "Do you understand me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 242600.0,
      "end_time": 244520.0,
      "text": "You may not come near me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 244520.0,
      "end_time": 246440.0,
      "text": "I am Erica Kane"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 246440.0,
      "end_time": 249080.0,
      "text": "and you are a filthy beast!&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249080.0,
      "end_time": 250920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250920.0,
      "end_time": 252600.0,
      "text": "And of course the bear left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 252600.0,
      "end_time": 254440.0,
      "text": "so what that teaches us"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 254440.0,
      "end_time": 256520.0,
      "text": "is obstacles are to be expected"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256519.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261239.99999999997,
      "text": "and we can choose to surrender or we can stand and fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 261240.0,
      "end_time": 264080.0,
      "text": "Pandora&#39;s Tim Westergren knows this better than most."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 264080.0,
      "end_time": 268000.0,
      "text": "You might even call him the Erica Kane of Silicon Valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 268000.0,
      "end_time": 270079.0,
      "text": "Tim and his cofounders launched the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 270079.0,
      "end_time": 271839.0,
      "text": "with two million dollars in funding."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271839.0,
      "end_time": 274840.0,
      "text": "They were out of cash the next year."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 274840.0,
      "end_time": 278600.0,
      "text": "Now, lots of companies fold at that point, but Tim chose to fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 278600.0,
      "end_time": 282800.0,
      "text": "He maxed out 11 credit cards and racked up six figures in personal debt"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 282800.0,
      "end_time": 284680.0,
      "text": "and it still wasn&#39;t enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 284680.0,
      "end_time": 289560.0,
      "text": "So every two weeks for two years on payday he stood in front of his employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 289560.0,
      "end_time": 293120.0,
      "text": "and he asked them to sacrifice their salaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 293120.0,
      "end_time": 294520.0,
      "text": "and it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 294520.0,
      "end_time": 297360.0,
      "text": "More than 50 people deferred two million dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 297360.0,
      "end_time": 299240.0,
      "text": "and now, more than a decade later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 299240.0,
      "end_time": 302360.0,
      "text": "Pandora is worth billions."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 302360.0,
      "end_time": 304840.0,
      "text": "When you believe that there is a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 304840.0,
      "end_time": 307240.0,
      "text": "around or through whatever is in front of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 307240.0,
      "end_time": 309800.0,
      "text": "that surrender is not an option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 313960.0,
      "text": "you can overcome enormous obstacles."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 313960.0,
      "end_time": 315960.0,
      "text": "Which brings us to soap opera lesson two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 315960.0,
      "end_time": 320720.0,
      "text": "sacrifice your ego and drop the superiority complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 320720.0,
      "end_time": 322320.0,
      "text": "Now, this is scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322320.0,
      "end_time": 325520.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an acknowledgment of need or fallibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 325520.0,
      "end_time": 326920.0,
      "text": "Maybe it&#39;s even an admission"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 326920.0,
      "end_time": 331120.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re not as special as we might like to think."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 331120.0,
      "end_time": 333560.0,
      "text": "Stephanie Forrester of &quot;The Bold and the Beautiful&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 333560.0,
      "end_time": 335320.0,
      "text": "thought she was pretty darn special."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335320.0,
      "end_time": 336840.0,
      "text": "She thought she was so special,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 336840.0,
      "end_time": 339560.0,
      "text": "she didn&#39;t need to mix with the riffraff from the valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 339560.0,
      "end_time": 342440.0,
      "text": "and she made sure valley girl Brooke knew it."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 342440.0,
      "end_time": 345880.0,
      "text": "But after nearly 25 years of epic fighting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 345880.0,
      "end_time": 349480.0,
      "text": "Stephanie got sick and let Brooke in."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 349480.0,
      "end_time": 350720.0,
      "text": "They made amends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 350720.0,
      "end_time": 352760.0,
      "text": "archenemies became soul mates"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 352760.0,
      "end_time": 355120.0,
      "text": "and Stephanie died in Brooke&#39;s arms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 355120.0,
      "end_time": 357440.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s our takeaway."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 357440.0,
      "end_time": 359000.0,
      "text": "Drop your ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 359000.0,
      "end_time": 360920.0,
      "text": "Life is not about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 360920.0,
      "end_time": 362560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 362560.0,
      "end_time": 365400.0,
      "text": "and our ability to experience joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 365400.0,
      "end_time": 367920.0,
      "text": "and love and to improve our reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 367920.0,
      "end_time": 370960.0,
      "text": "comes only when we make ourselves vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 370960.0,
      "end_time": 374120.0,
      "text": "and we accept responsibility for our actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 374120.0,
      "end_time": 375520.0,
      "text": "and our inactions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 375520.0,
      "end_time": 378920.0,
      "text": "kind of like Howard Schultz, the CEO of Starbucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 378920.0,
      "end_time": 380960.0,
      "text": "Now, after a great run as CEO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 380960.0,
      "end_time": 383280.0,
      "text": "Howard stepped down in 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 383280.0,
      "end_time": 385520.0,
      "text": "and Starbucks quickly overextended itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 385520.0,
      "end_time": 387520.0,
      "text": "and stock prices fell."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 387520.0,
      "end_time": 389480.0,
      "text": "Howard rejoined the team in 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 389480.0,
      "end_time": 391520.0,
      "text": "and one of the first things he did"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 391520.0,
      "end_time": 396920.0,
      "text": "was apologize to all 180,000 employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 396920.0,
      "end_time": 398800.0,
      "text": "He apologized."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 398800.0,
      "end_time": 402800.0,
      "text": "And then he asked for help, honesty, and ideas in return."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 405400.0,
      "text": "And now, Starbucks has more than doubled"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 405400.0,
      "end_time": 408160.0,
      "text": "its net revenue since Howard came back."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 408160.0,
      "end_time": 412120.0,
      "text": "So sacrifice your desire to be right or safe all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 412120.0,
      "end_time": 415240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not helping anyone, least of all you."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 415240.0,
      "end_time": 419240.0,
      "text": "Sacrifice your ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 419240.0,
      "end_time": 420720.0,
      "text": "Soap opera lesson three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 420720.0,
      "end_time": 424240.0,
      "text": "evolution is real."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 424240.0,
      "end_time": 426960.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not meant to be static characters."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 426960.0,
      "end_time": 430920.0,
      "text": "On television, static equals boring and boring equals fired."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 430920.0,
      "end_time": 434560.0,
      "text": "Characters are supposed to grow and change."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 434560.0,
      "end_time": 437040.0,
      "text": "Now, on TV, those dynamic changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 437040.0,
      "end_time": 439320.0,
      "text": "can make for some rough transitions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 439320.0,
      "end_time": 442720.0,
      "text": "particularly when a character is played by one person yesterday"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 442720.0,
      "end_time": 445840.0,
      "text": "and played by someone new today."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 445840.0,
      "end_time": 449560.0,
      "text": "Recasting happens all the time on soaps."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 449560.0,
      "end_time": 451400.0,
      "text": "Over the last 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 451400.0,
      "end_time": 454280.0,
      "text": "four different actors have played the same key role"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 454280.0,
      "end_time": 457720.0,
      "text": "of Carly Benson on &quot;General Hospital.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 457720.0,
      "end_time": 462880.0,
      "text": "Each new face triggered a change in the character&#39;s life and personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 462880.0,
      "end_time": 466960.0,
      "text": "Now, there was always an essential nugget of Carly in there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 466960.0,
      "end_time": 471640.0,
      "text": "but the character and the story adapted to whomever was playing her."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 471640.0,
      "end_time": 474400.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s what that means for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 474400.0,
      "end_time": 477040.0,
      "text": "While we may not swap faces in our own lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 477040.0,
      "end_time": 478960.0,
      "text": "we can evolve too."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 478960.0,
      "end_time": 484320.0,
      "text": "We can choose to draw a circle around our feet and stay in that spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 484320.0,
      "end_time": 486880.0,
      "text": "or we can open ourselves to opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 486880.0,
      "end_time": 491520.0,
      "text": "like Carly, who went from nursing student to hotel owner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 491520.0,
      "end_time": 493720.0,
      "text": "or like Julia Child."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 493720.0,
      "end_time": 496400.0,
      "text": "Julia was a World War II spy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 496400.0,
      "end_time": 499760.0,
      "text": "and when the war ended, she got married, moved to France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 499760.0,
      "end_time": 503080.0,
      "text": "and decided to give culinary school a shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 503080.0,
      "end_time": 509640.0,
      "text": "Julia, her books and her TV shows revolutionized the way America cooks."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 509640.0,
      "end_time": 512960.0,
      "text": "We all have the power to initiate change in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 512960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515560.00000000006,
      "text": "to evolve and adapt."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 515559.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517399.99999999994,
      "text": "We make the choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 517400.0,
      "end_time": 521000.0,
      "text": "but sometimes life chooses for us, and we don&#39;t get a heads up."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 521000.0,
      "end_time": 523200.0,
      "text": "Surprise slams us in the face."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 523200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525360.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re flat on the ground, the air is gone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 525360.0,
      "end_time": 527960.0,
      "text": "and you need resuscitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 527960.0,
      "end_time": 531159.0,
      "text": "So thank goodness for soap opera lesson four:"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 531159.0,
      "end_time": 533440.0,
      "text": "resurrection is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 533440.0,
      "end_time": 534880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 534880.0,
      "end_time": 538960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 538960.0,
      "end_time": 543160.0,
      "text": "In 1983, &quot;Days of Our Lives&quot;&#39; Stefano DiMera died of a stroke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 543160.0,
      "end_time": 545720.0,
      "text": "but not really, because in 1984"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 545720.0,
      "end_time": 548480.0,
      "text": "he died when his car plunged into the harbor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 548480.0,
      "end_time": 552040.0,
      "text": "and yet he was back in 1985 with a brain tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 552040.0,
      "end_time": 553080.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 553080.0,
      "end_time": 555720.0,
      "text": "But before the tumor could kill him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 555720.0,
      "end_time": 560440.0,
      "text": "Marlena shot him, and he tumbled off a catwalk to his death."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 560440.0,
      "end_time": 562760.0,
      "text": "And so it went for 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 562760.0,
      "end_time": 565280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 565280.0,
      "end_time": 567440.0,
      "text": "Even when we saw the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 567440.0,
      "end_time": 568680.0,
      "text": "we knew better."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 568680.0,
      "end_time": 572720.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s called the Phoenix for a reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 572720.0,
      "end_time": 575000.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s what that means for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 575000.0,
      "end_time": 577480.0,
      "text": "As long as the show is still on the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 577480.0,
      "end_time": 579600.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re still breathing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 579600.0,
      "end_time": 581280.0,
      "text": "nothing is permanent."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 581280.0,
      "end_time": 585560.0,
      "text": "Resurrection is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 585560.0,
      "end_time": 588280.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, just like life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 588280.0,
      "end_time": 592320.0,
      "text": "soap operas do ultimately meet the big finale."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 592320.0,
      "end_time": 597280.0,
      "text": "CBS canceled my show, &quot;As The World Turns,&quot; in December 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 597280.0,
      "end_time": 598880.0,
      "text": "and we shot our final episode"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 598880.0,
      "end_time": 600640.0,
      "text": "in June 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 600640.0,
      "end_time": 602360.0,
      "text": "It was six months of dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 602360.0,
      "end_time": 606240.0,
      "text": "and I rode that train right into the mountain."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 606240.0,
      "end_time": 609000.0,
      "text": "And even though we were in the middle of a huge recession"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 609000.0,
      "end_time": 612840.0,
      "text": "and millions of people were struggling to find work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 612840.0,
      "end_time": 615160.0,
      "text": "I somehow thought everything would be OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 615160.0,
      "end_time": 617880.0,
      "text": "So I packed up the kids and the Brooklyn apartment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 617880.0,
      "end_time": 620240.0,
      "text": "and we moved in with my in-laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 620240.0,
      "end_time": 621480.0,
      "text": "in Alabama."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 621480.0,
      "end_time": 624920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 624920.0,
      "end_time": 627680.0,
      "text": "Three months later, nothing was OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 627680.0,
      "end_time": 632920.0,
      "text": "That was when I watched the final episode air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 632920.0,
      "end_time": 637040.0,
      "text": "and I realized the show was not the only fatality."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 637040.0,
      "end_time": 639120.0,
      "text": "I was one too."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 639120.0,
      "end_time": 641720.0,
      "text": "I was unemployed and living on the second floor"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 641720.0,
      "end_time": 643320.0,
      "text": "of my in-laws&#39; home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 643320.0,
      "end_time": 646120.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s enough to make anyone feel dead inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 646120.0,
      "end_time": 648040.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 648040.0,
      "end_time": 650200.0,
      "text": "But I knew my story wasn&#39;t over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 650200.0,
      "end_time": 652440.0,
      "text": "that it couldn&#39;t be over."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 652440.0,
      "end_time": 658360.0,
      "text": "I just had to tap into everything I had ever learned about soap operas."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 658360.0,
      "end_time": 661920.0,
      "text": "I had to be brave like Erica and refuse to surrender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 661920.0,
      "end_time": 666000.0,
      "text": "so every day, I made a decision to fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 666000.0,
      "end_time": 668600.0,
      "text": "I had to be vulnerable like Stephanie"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 668600.0,
      "end_time": 670160.0,
      "text": "and sacrifice my ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 674760.0,
      "text": "I had to ask for help a lot of times across many states."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 674760.0,
      "end_time": 678240.0,
      "text": "I had to be adaptable like Carly"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 678240.0,
      "end_time": 681800.0,
      "text": "and evolve my skills, my mindset, and my circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 681800.0,
      "end_time": 684800.0,
      "text": "and then I had to be resilient, like Stefano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 684800.0,
      "end_time": 687480.0,
      "text": "and resurrect myself and my career"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 687480.0,
      "end_time": 690760.0,
      "text": "like a phoenix from the ashes."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 690760.0,
      "end_time": 693640.0,
      "text": "Eventually I got an interview."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 693640.0,
      "end_time": 696600.0,
      "text": "After 15 years in news and entertainment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 696600.0,
      "end_time": 698560.0,
      "text": "nine months of unemployment"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 698560.0,
      "end_time": 701840.0,
      "text": "and this one interview,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 701840.0,
      "end_time": 705040.0,
      "text": "I had an offer for an entry level job."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 705040.0,
      "end_time": 706920.0,
      "text": "I was 37 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 706920.0,
      "end_time": 710240.0,
      "text": "and I was back from the dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 710240.0,
      "end_time": 713360.0,
      "text": "We will all experience what looks like an ending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 713360.0,
      "end_time": 716120.0,
      "text": "and we can choose to make it a beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 716120.0,
      "end_time": 720240.0,
      "text": "Kind of like Tina, who miraculously survived that waterfall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 720240.0,
      "end_time": 722960.0,
      "text": "and because I hate to leave a cliffhanger hanging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 722960.0,
      "end_time": 725160.0,
      "text": "Tina and Cord did get divorced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 725160.0,
      "end_time": 731080.0,
      "text": "but they got remarried three times before the show went off the air in 2012."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 731080.0,
      "end_time": 732840.0,
      "text": "So remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 732840.0,
      "end_time": 736320.0,
      "text": "as long as there is breath in your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 736320.0,
      "end_time": 739480.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s never too late to change your story."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 739480.0,
      "end_time": 740720.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 740720.0,
      "end_time": 750720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}